text: Miliusa zeylanica is a species of plant in the Annonaceae family. It is endemic to Sri Lanka. ==References== * World Conservation Monitoring Centre 1998. Miliusa zeylanica. 2006 IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. Downloaded on 22 August 2007.
